column1: "Apnader platinum er J service ta kivabe nite parbo"
"Under construction er somoy nite hobe naki puritan finishing Howard port?"
"Please send some room decorations catalog with price"
"How can I avail Online Interior Design Consultation?"
"You missed a video chat with Monir."

"I would like to decor my bedroom. But right now I am outside Bangladesh. So, my mother will look after everything. Is it possible you visit my home this week and give me a sample how can I decor my bedroom? I will be in BD in two weeks but want to start decor before I arrive."
"May I know about the price of  doing one bedroom decor?"
"I believe all of these can happen after you see my bedroom. I haven't seen my room as well coz I live abroad. But when I return I want to live in a cosy nice bedroom. So that's why I choose you."
"may I know how many days it would take the minimum to decorate one bedroom?"
"I will give you my mother number and home address. Could you please contact with her?"
"I don't have any particular requirements so if you could provide me a sample it would be great."

"Nasima Akhter 
Mobile: +880 19 2383 7675

Address: House-07, Road-02, Sector-03 , Tushardhara, Matuail Kadamtoli, Dhaka-1362"
